9 Named for the Gani-Gabi indigenous peoples who have special reverence for the Glasshouse Mountains. subapical in position, ventral surface with 2 apical spurs. Genicular lobes of fore and middle femora unarmed; hind femur armed or not on internal lobe with a minute spine. Abdomen slender, tenth tergite with soft, membranous median portion; paraprocts not unusually produced. 
